:{"pid":"06df2c04dc57440368fa7d414912dd299d908ef1","tid":1408724,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:15:00.000Z","msg":"黑B<br />\n<br />\ndeadline 9 點半囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:15:14.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bbcc8c421d97d4b6788d9cb6fd9c400c4a8acaa","tid":1408724,"uid":60716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:15:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c224f30f7a035654caf90df48497f95121a76064","tid":1408724,"uid":2617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:16:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真。最後(?)<br />\n大家有需要可以轉發/整圖/乜柒都好</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人對政府發出最後通牒<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n<br />\n就香港政府持續昏庸無能，香港人今日（八月五日）作出嚴正聲明：<br />\n<br />\n修訂《逃犯條例》引發香港最嚴重之政治風波，惟政府毫無悔意，多次錯過解決風波的時機，終令示威活動遍地開花。<br />\n<br />\n- 六月九日一百萬人上街遊行，政府表示條例「如期二讀」；<br />\n- 六月十六日二百萬人再上街，政府無意就六一二事件展開獨立調查；<br />\n- 七月一日香港人重奪議會，政府只顧凌晨開記者會譴責，毫無反省，不知愧恥；<br />\n- 七月二十一日元朗發生恐襲，政府翌日方見記者，卻先譴責示威者侮辱中共國徽。<br />\n<br />\n政府多次犯下彌天大錯，且對黑警濫權及造反視若無睹，香港人已清楚指出，「We are saving Hong Kong, not rioting」。政府無為程度已遠遠超越正常人的底線，將香港推向極為危險的邊緣，香港人絕不能縱容。<br />\n<br />\n香港今日極大規模的示威活動，乃對政府之發出最後通牒，促請政府切勿與民為敵，不再龜縮，於今晨九時半前直接且正面回應示威者五大訴求：<br />\n<br />\n- 正式撤回《逃犯條例》修訂；<br />\n- 撤回所有示威暴動定性；<br />\n- 撤銷所有抗爭者控罪，不可秋後算帳；<br />\n- 成立獨立調查委員會，調查警察濫暴濫權、追究警察開槍責任及元朗警黑勾結；<br />\n- 全面落實雙普選。<br />\n<br />\n香港人此時此刻於各區的示威，已展示人民對政府極度憤恨。這是一個關鍵的時刻，政府必須以香港整體利益為依歸，於今晨九時半前回應市民，否則後果自負！香港人將嚴厲追究，向政府說「不」。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n2019年8月5日（星期一）<br />\n香港時間2時05分"},{"pid":"0fb6942e953a6679af7d878f8d994b02a9d42774","tid":1408724,"uid":72693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ycbOsDp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FycbOsDp.gif&h=78e52dbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n環保啲用返先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906af24289b8633b5e250c16525901c25b5860a3","tid":1408724,"uid":26441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:17:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"60afb6616fcc6bb3b17e2eb00bd1b97cf4fde347","tid":1408724,"uid":53601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07f945d4c330235669dc5ba82485ebdec55eaea6","tid":1408724,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:13:37.000Z","msg":"條撚樣好似9半開記招<br />\n駛唔駛再早D"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:17:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58a9704abc5ea577b9339117ecaa1f7622b4e66","tid":1408724,"uid":216253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b7267452e83856583c1154a5d96293683b47fd","tid":1408724,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60afb6616fcc6bb3b17e2eb00bd1b97cf4fde347","tid":1408724,"uid":53601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07f945d4c330235669dc5ba82485ebdec55eaea6","tid":1408724,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:13:37.000Z","msg":"條撚樣好似9半開記招<br />\n駛唔駛再早D"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:17:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:18:34.000Z","msg":"我一路執緊了"},{"pid":"69b583c4809a8c97ade188e95dea6c6450f410ad","tid":1408724,"uid":168818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:18:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a127d96da5dfc9d2915965f5e35a66c21584d7","tid":1408724,"uid":11388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\